Building binary packages for Debian:

0. Prerequisites:
	Packages libssl-dev, libexpat1-dev, and libreadline5-dev must be installed

1. Configure and build NetXMS as following:

	./configure --prefix=/usr --with-server --with-odbc --with-sqlite --with-pgsql --with-mysql
	make install

2. Go to packages/linux/debian

3. Run populate.sh <version>

4. Run build.sh

5. Resulting .deb files will be in output directory
